data.title: Water Street Auto :: Cambridge ON Tires & Auto Repair Shop
data.meta_description: Water Street Auto is a tire dealer and auto repair shop in Cambridge ON. Water Street Auto has deals on Cambridge ON tires, auto repairs and wheels. Save at Water Street Auto!
data.text:
Welcome to Water Street Auto Ltd.

Our doors at Water Street Auto Ltd. first opened in 1990. Located at 55 Water St. South in Cambridge, ON, we provide honest and thorough automotive repairs and tire sales to customers from Cambridge, ON, Kitchener, ON, Guelph, ON, and surrounding areas. The pride of Water Street Auto Ltd. is our incredible customer service and our experienced staff of automotive professionals who are capable of performing quality auto repairs. Our technicians are ready to return the dependability to your vehicle. As a tire dealer, we carry some of the most respected tire brands in the industry, including tires from MICHELINÂ®, Firestone, and Bridgestone. Open Monday through Friday 7:30 AM - 5:00 PM , and closed on long weekends and special holidays. We look forward to providing extensive auto repairs, tire sales, and exceptional customer service to all of our customers.

About Us For over 29 years, Water Street Auto Ltd. has been a pillar of the Cambridge, ON community. Water Street Auto Ltd. is a leader in offering name brand tires, auto repair services for customers located in and around the Cambridge, Ontario area. Our goal is to focus on customer service. It is the foundation of our business. Water Street Auto Ltd. employs a well-trained staff specializing in the sale and installation of passenger car, performance, light truck, or SUV tires. Take this opportunity to browse Water Street Auto Ltd. website or call us for personalized service.
